{
  "stem": "10181.3",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we got to the train, which was-- it wasn't the regular train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was one of those cattle wagons with straw on the floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put 80 or whatever people on the-- on the wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I screamed very loudly, and my cousin screamed because I started to scream.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a lot of people were wailing and crying, so it wasn't anything special, but maybe, could be that I screamed louder.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I know some German guard went to a Dutch policeman, asked what the-- what the commotion was all about.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Dutch policeman said, I-- I guess he doesn't want to go on this train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the-- the German policeman said to [? the guard, ?] then take him off immediately.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's too much commotion, you know, and I don't like it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was taken off the train together with my cousin and put aside, you know, till the train left.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were kept in sort of a holding place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were some other people taken off the train, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I wasn't the only one, but they were taken for different reasons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were taken off because at the last moment, the commandants decided that their deferment was still good and they shouldn't go, or they had good connections with-- with-- with the Jewish commandant-- there was a Jewish commandant, too.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And maybe he knew them and tried to get them off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So a few other people were taken off because they were privileged.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I was taken off with my cousin because I'd screamed-- for no other reason.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Of course, this-- I found out years later, this particular train went to Sobibor and nobody survived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nobody came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Very few Jews survived Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Sobibor was a death camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
